http://www.thehindu.com/business/Economy/RBI-sets-rupee-reference-rate-at-67.6428-against-dollar/article14019519.ece

The Reserve Bank of India on Monday fixed the reference rate of the rupee at 67.6428 against the US dollar and 73.1219 for the euro.These rates were 67.7480 and 73.4050, respectively, on Friday.According to an RBI statement, the exchange rates for the pound and the yen against the rupee were quoted at 96.7360 and 56.93 per 100 yens, respectively, based on reference rates for the dollar and cross-currency quotes at noon.The SDR-rupee rate will be based on this rate, the statement added.